text: Brett Zuijdwegt (born 15 February 1999) is a Dutch korfball player. She is a member of PKC and the Netherlands national korfball team. With the national team she won the gold medal at the 2022 World Games in Birmingham, Alabama. ==Achievements== ===Club=== *Korfbal League champion, 1x (2021) * champion, 1x (2022) ===National team=== *World Games champion, 1x (2022) *European champion, 1x (2021) ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch korfball players Category:Sportspeople from Dordrecht Category:Sportswomen
